OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1772547083
OL,3,CPolice admit they might take your car
OL,4,Ckeys to protect you from theft
OL,6,FOver just four hours, police found
OL,7,Fnearly 50 insecure vehicles, which
OL,8,Fthey say highlights "the scale of
OL,9,Fpreventable opportunity".
OL,11,FSt Helier and St Saviour are the main
OL,12,Fhotspots, with 85% of vehicle thefts
OL,13,Frecorded in those parishes, although
OL,14,Fthe force adds, "stolen vehicles are
OL,15,Foften driven across the island, making
OL,16,Fthis an islandwide issue".
OL,18,FTheir radical step is to take the car
OL,19,Fkeys first, so someone with bad
OL,20,Fintentions cannot.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
