OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1772547083
OL,3,CPolice admit they might take your car
OL,4,Ckeys to protect you from theft
OL,6,F"Operation Handle is about stopping
OL,7,Fpreventable crime before someone gets
OL,8,Fkilled," Chief Inspector Craig Jackson
OL,9,Fexplains.
OL,11,F"We're carrying out targeted patrols
OL,12,Fin highrisk areas, using covert and
OL,13,Fplainclothes tactics where required,
OL,14,Fcontacting owners of insecure vehicles
OL,15,Fand, when necessary, removing keys so
OL,16,Fthose cars can't be stolen and driven
OL,17,Fdangerously."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1772547083
OL,3,CPolice admit they might take your car
OL,4,Ckeys to protect you from theft
OL,6,FThe police admit that they do not want
OL,7,Fto be doing this, but they are
OL,8,Fresponding to an increased risk to
OL,9,Fislanders.
OL,11,FThey aim to reduce repeat youth
OL,12,Foffending and vehicle crime, whilst
OL,13,Fpreventing a serious accident.
OL,15,F"Our biggest risk is complacency,"
OL,16,FChief Inspector Jackson adds.
OL,18,F"Every insecure vehicle is an
OL,19,Fopportunity and the next stolen car
OL,20,Fcould be the one involved in a fatal
OL,21,Fcollision.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1772547083
OL,3,CPolice admit they might take your car
OL,4,Ckeys to protect you from theft
OL,6,F"The aim is to prevent harm, not wait
OL,7,Ffor it."
OL,9,FThe move has sparked a debate on
OL,10,Fsocial media, with some questioning
OL,11,Fthe legality of what the police are
OL,12,Fdoing and whether they would, in fact,
OL,13,Fbe committing a crime themselves by
OL,14,Ftaking away the keys.
OL,16,FHowever, the force maintains that what
OL,17,Fit is doing is legal and proportionate
OL,18,Fas "a last resort".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
