OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1772547083
OL,3,CPolice admit they might take your car
OL,4,Ckeys to protect you from theft
OL,6,FOne social media user commented, "That
OL,7,Fwould be an absolutely disgusting
OL,8,Finvasion on our freedom".
OL,10,FAnother said, "What's wrong with
OL,11,Fpeople taking responsibility for their
OL,12,Fown property?"
OL,14,FA third stated, "The Police are trying
OL,15,Fto reduce crime. Support them, don't
OL,16,Fput them down, their hard work is
OL,17,Falways appreciated."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
